Package: hfutils
Type: Package
Title: Core Utilities for the Hydrofabric Stack
Description: Base-layer utilities for accessing, cleaning, summarizing, and
    versioning hydrofabric datasets. Provides hydrofabric I/O (GeoPackage,
    GeoParquet, and lazy GDAL/OGR-SQL access), DEM-derived geometry cleaning,
    network and topology algorithms (downstream accumulation, hydrosequence),
    staged pipeline invariant checks, and GeoPackage dataset-version and
    provenance metadata helpers used across the hydrofabric package suite.
Version: 0.3.4
